=head1 DESCRIPTION

A custom type that specifies a C<Region> and the C<KmsKeyId> for a
replica secret.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 KmsKeyId => Str

The ARN, key ID, or alias of the KMS key to encrypt the secret. If you
don't include this field, Secrets Manager uses C<aws/secretsmanager>.


=head2 Region => Str

